title: Ezgi Ömüriş and Mehmet Sinan Özdemir – De floreo by Solo Tango

description:
Ezgi Ömüriş and Mehmet Sinan Özdemir dance “De floreo” played live by Solo Tango Orquesta at the 1st Sultans of Istanbul Tango Festival 2016 in Istanbul, Turkey.
